{
  "stem": "20083.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was nothing to discuss anymore-- I mean, just the usual maternal warnings-- be careful when you cross the street and never speak with your mouth full and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But generally speaking, it was not very eventful or melodramatic conversation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The only thing is that when we hugged at the [GERMAN], at the station and said goodbye to each other, that all three of us cried.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember walking down a long hallway and turning around once more and my sister and my mother waving to me in their winter coats.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was last I saw of my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But of course, my sister was saved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I saw her later, long after the war again, in the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Kindertransport-- there probably were 50 or 60 boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were my age and younger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The youngest probably was around four or five years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we took the train to the Dutch border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While we waited on the German side, we had SS troops surrounding our compartments so that none of us could escape, as if we wanted to escape back into Nazi Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as I recall-- because the compartments-- we had our own compartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There are usually six or eight people per compartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were just boys and girls in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was nobody in my personal compartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot remember today whether the entire lot of 60 or 70 boys and girls-- whether there was a supervisor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I simply cannot remember, because we were put on the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train went to Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once we reached the Dutch border and crossed into Holland, we started singing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We started laughing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the SS had left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was freedom for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
